public interface StockQuoteInterface
This interface will return pertinent information about a given stock quote.

    • getSymbol

      String getSymbol()
      This will return the stock symbol for the given quote.
      Returns:
      the symbol

    • getLastTradingPrice

      double getLastTradingPrice()
      This will return the last trading price for the stock. If the market is open, this is the price that the stock is currently selling for. If the market is closed, it is the price from the last sale of the stock.
      Returns:
      the lastTrade.

    • getPreviousClose

      double getPreviousClose()
      This will return the previous close on the stock. This is the amount that the stock sold for at the close of the last trading session, typically the day before.
      Returns:
      the close

    • getChange

      double getChange()
      This will return the changed value for the given stock versus the previous close.
      Returns:
      The return will be the absolute change in dollars and cents for the given stock. The value will be given in dollars and cents as a double, with the dollars being to the left of the decimal point and the cents being to the right.
